Students must have an internship offer prior to registering for this course.  The Experiential Learning Center (Tivoli 260) provides information, resources and assistance with searching and applying for internships.  All students must meet with an internship advisor to register for this course.  For more information, go to www.ucdenver.edu/elc  or contact the Experiential Learning Center at 303.556.6656.
